(1, 2, 0, '2009-04-03', 'A Bari O Bari', '1.jpg', '1.flv', 'Every Tuesday 9.00 PM', '', 'Nazrul Islam Siddique', 'A.Z. Firoj', '', '', 'Ajijul Hakim, Tania Ahmed, Shahriar Nazim Joy, Tanima Hamid, Chitrolekha Guho, Fakhrul Hasan Bairagi', 'This is a comedy drama between two adjacent families. The head of this family is Fakir Ful Mia, a business man having three sons and a couple servants. Mr. Fakir has enforced a strict instruction that there will be no love and marriage in this family. On the other hand the head of that family is Anguri Begum who is celibate. Her family members are her elder niece Dina, younger niece Rina and an unemployed brother Felu. But the younger generation of both families can’t follow the instructions any longer; they began to love and took many funny activities to continue their relationship. The head persons of both families blamed each other for this. But once they could realize the depth and nobility of love. Then they withdraw their instructions and a relationship established between this two families.'),
(2, 2, 0, '2009-04-03', 'Alta Shundori', '2a.jpg', '2a.flv', 'Thursday & Friday 9.25 PM', '', 'Brindabon Das', 'Salahuddin Lavlu', '', '', 'Chanchal Choudhury, Shamim Zaman, Lara Lotus and more', 'A young guy named Lausser works in a musical theatre group, and he plays the role of "Alta Shundori". As female theatre worker is rarely available so Lausser has to play the role in disguise of a lady. Another young guy named Rahim Badsha becomes mad about Lausser for his singing, dancing and acting. At that time a gambler named “Juari” started gambling in the function of the group. And a conflict between “Alta Sundori” and “Juari” got started. And at the end of the game “Alta Sundori” won, and this is how the artists of the fair succession survive by struggle.'),
(3, 2, 0, '2009-05-24', 'Apon Ghorey Porobash', '3.jpg', '3.flv', 'Sturday 9:50 PM', '', 'Aftab bin Tamiz', 'Kaisar Ahmed', '', '', 'Sahiduzzaman Selim, Tania Ahmed, Shoeb, Joy, Srabonty, Dipa Khandakar, A T M Shamsuzzaman, Chitralekha Guha, Faruk Ahmed etc.', 'Bikar Khan head of a higher middle class family In the family there are his wife Aina Begom and two daughter Antara and Shamoly, two sarvents and his brother in law, it seems as a parlament. Monir and Emran recently passed from University are searching for job and accommodation. They make a plan being rich man will have to marry rich daughter of a rich father for this why they rent a house in front of Auntara and Sanchari`s house. Suddenly Bikar khan announced that a new guest are coming from America but can`t know the name now . every body are waiting and at the end of drama they came to know that the guest Nilla are nobody but the daughter of Bikar khan`s previous wife and she is the owner of this house.  By this way the serial end. '),
(4, 2, 0, '2009-05-24', 'F D C', '4c.jpg', '4c.flv', 'Saturday & Sunday 09:45 PM', '', 'Kochi Khandker', 'Kochi Khandker', '', '', 'Jahid Hasan, Anisur rahman Milon, Lutfor Rahman George, Shahiduzzaman Salim, Film star Riaj,Mousumi, Shabnur, Purnima, Shakib khan and many more', 'Liaqat Ali Liku, a simple village guy is a fan of cine-world in Bangladesh. He never fails to watch any movie released in the local cinema halls in his area. This can be said that he becomes a sort of cine specialist that can easily mimic the expression of any hero and so on. Out of curiosity to see the heroines, once he went to F.D.C. There he met with a cine-journalist Shwapan Nandy. At first he under estimated Shwapan but after some times his conception became changed about him. And he got his shelter in Shwapan’s shack. He came to know about his love and strong connections of F.D.C. Liku got his entrance to F.D.C with the help of Shwapan.'),
(5, 2, 0, '2009-05-24', 'Mayati Akhon Kothay Jabe', '5.jpg', '5.flv', 'Sunday and Monday 9:00 PM', '', 'Imdadul Haque Milon', 'Shanjit Sarkar', '', '', 'Shahed, Kusum Sikder, Abul Hayat, Doly Johur', 'Mr. Gani is the father of two daughters Hena and Bina. Hena uses to go to college on foot and often faces obstacles by a spoilt guy named Raja. He proposed Hena to marry and she refused him, then he kidnaped her. Then the family members of Raja compelled him to set her free. Hena went her home but her father denied to accept her. Now what will happen to her.......this is the story of this drama. This drama is written by Imdadul Haque Milon and Directed by Shanjit Sarkar.'),
(6, 2, 0, '2009-05-24', 'Priodorshini', '6.jpg', '6.flv', '', '', 'Pranab Vatta (Episode - Nazrul Islam & Aurun Chaudhury)', 'Aurun Chaoudhury', '', '', 'Dilara zaman, Subarna Mostafa, Tazin Ahmed etc.', 'The story of women`s life, her joys, sorrows with all these “priodarshini” are going of 52 episodes serial.Through the story are open out different mind set of women`s life . This women are either mother, daughter, sister, wife or lover. In one side mother is looking for her missing daughter another side daughter find someone else and develop her new life, fall in love . In the other hand husband wife`s conflicts.'),
(7, 4, 0, '2009-05-24', 'Robi Jege Acho Ki?', '7j.jpg', '7j.flv', 'Saturday 11:30 PM', '', '', '', 'Sohel Rana (Bidduth)', '', '', 'Its almost midnight, you are in bed but can’t sleep! No tension! Sayem and Nafiza is there to chat with you. You can call or you can send sms and emails to share your deepest thought with the presenters and at the same time you can play your favorite singer''s song from Rtv studio. It is also a good opportunity to listen live conversation among Sayem, Nafiza and one of your favorite celebrities where the celebrity shares his/her unspoken private emotions on the show.<br><br>Our contact: Phone- <b>8159355-9</b>, for sms type <b>jak</b>, write your message and send it to <b>4141</b> from any mobile operator, and our e-mail address is: <b>jegeachoki@rtvbd.tv</b>'),
