(12, 4, 0, '2009-05-24', 'Drishshokolpo', '12b.jpg', '12b.flv', 'Monday 11:30 PM (Fortnightly)', '', '', '', 'Syed Shabab Ali Arzoo', '', '', 'This program is a sort of critic discussion about the classic movies, or movies made by the world famous directors. The discussion topics are the story, screen play, photography, art direction, music of a movie. Besides discussion, remarkable scenes or clippings are shown on the program.'),
(13, 4, 0, '2009-05-24', 'Jibone Jibon Ano', '13b.jpg', '13b.flv', 'Friday 11:30 PM', '', '', '', 'Rowshon Ara Nipa', '', '', 'This is a phono-live talkshow - based on the topics of the complications of drug addiction, HIV/AIDS. Through this program, the specialized personnels give the counseling to the suffered guy over phone. Besides they also give suggestions relating to the routine life according to the ques of the viewers. Viewers are asked to leave their questions over phone and the contact no is <b>8159355-7</b>.'),
(14, 4, 1, '2009-05-24', 'প্রাণ মি: ম্যাংগো তারকালাপ', '14j.jpg', 'hRIkswBMzD0', 'প্রতিদিন সকাল ১০:৪০ মিনিটে', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'বিস্তারিত জানতে ভিডিও দেখুন'),
(15, 4, 0, '2009-05-24', 'Nari O Nakhkhtro', '15c.jpg', '15c.flv', 'Tuesday 6:30 PM', '22 minutes', '', '', 'Rowshon Ara Nipa', '', '', 'Every person expects his or her own identity. To achive her position in the society the women has to overcome many obstacle. To know or inform all these background story we are arranging the show Nari O Nakhatra.'),
(16, 7, 0, '2009-05-24', 'Sustho Thakun Protidin', '16f.jpg', '16f.flv', 'Sundat to Thursday 6:00 PM', '', '', '', 'Shahriar Islam', '', '', 'Sustho Thakun Protidin is the 1st ever daily live medical treatment program in Bangladesh. This is a daily health related program. In each episode, a doctor gives suggestions to the patients over phone and there is a fixed topic about health and disease in each episode. Viewers are asked to leave their questions over phone, and the contact number is <b>8159355-7</b>.'),
(17, 4, 0, '2009-05-24', 'Very Filmy', '17j.jpg', '17j.flv', 'Monday 12:05 PM', '', '', '', 'Tanif Mahmud', '', '', 'This is a live talk show related to Bangladeshi films. In each episode a relevant guest of film media is invited and viewers can talk to him over phone. And in this program, the host discusses with him about his contribution in this film media.'),
(18, 5, 0, '2009-05-24', 'News Cafe', '18.jpg', '18.flv', 'Everyday 12:00 AM', '', '', 'Anis Alamgir', 'Shikder Lotus Shabuj', '', '', 'A new talk-show named ''News Cafe'' based on analytical news is being aired on the popular satellite channel Rtv. Editors of the leading newspapers, prominent journalists and mass communication experts, politicians, economists, news and political critics, business leaders and celebrities of the society take part in discussion with the headlines of Rtv news at night and the important news of the following day''s different newspapers of the country. Besides, experts in the related important issues which are broadcast live participate with the talk show over telephone. This show turns a lots of viewers'' attention and becomes a very popular program at present for the details analysis of the news and current affairs.'),
(19, 4, 0, '2009-05-24', 'Walton Star and Sports', '19e.jpg', '19e.flv', 'Friday 06:00 PM', '', '', '', 'Shafiqul Islam Tutul', '', '', 'It''s a sports related program. Producing by Shafiqul Islam Tutul and presenting by Urmi Noor Binte Gias. This program is on air every Thursday at 6:30 p.m.'),
(20, 4, 0, '2009-05-24', 'Trade Talk', '20f.jpg', '20f.flv', 'Sunday 11:30 PM', '', '', '', 'Sohel H', '', '', 'Rtv presents weakly Business Talk Show "Trade Talk" where successful business idol come and discuss about the current business affairs. Through this program Viewers can get information about current business prospects, hurdles, and way of success.'),
(21, 7, 0, '2009-05-24', 'Ai Din', '21c.jpg', '21c.flv', 'Everyday 8:00 AM', '', '', '', 'Shahriar Islam', '', '', 'This is a daily program. The contents of this program are Health Tips, History info of Dhaka City, Info about Daily Recreation, Book review, Song, Poetry, Nutrition Tips and Daily Tips.'),
(22, 7, 0, '2009-05-24', 'Good Shot', '22b.jpg', '22b.flv', 'Monday 11:30 PM (Fortnightly)', '', '', '', 'Syed Shabab Ali Arzoo', 'Nazia Andaleeb Prema', '', 'Now a day a huge number of youth are working in visual media. The students of the department of Film & Media in various universities and the trainees of the Film Appreciation Course organized by different government or non-government organizations usually make short films. Those are either documentaries, fictions or cartoons, which don’t get appreciations. Through this program we invite those film makers with their productions (duration maximum 10 minutes), discuss them about their production.'),
(23, 7, 0, '2009-05-24', 'Grihoshoily', '23a.jpg', '23a.flv', 'Thursday 6:45 PM', '22 Minutes', '', '', 'Afroza Sulatana Choitty', '', '', '''The best home which is made by my self''. If your home style presents the beauty of art then you will feel peace in your mind and also presents your beautiful creative idea to others. All these artistic subjects includes in ''Grihoshaily''.'),
(24, 7, 0, '2009-05-24', 'Heart Beat', '24a.jpg', '24a.flv', 'Saturday 6:45 PM', '22 minutes', '', 'Shahriar Shakil', '', 'Dr. N.K. Natasha', '', 'This a kind of educative documentary related to health, medicine, surgery, hospital and etc. And many international hospitals and their way of treatment are shown in this program.'),
(25, 7, 0, '2009-05-24', 'Japito Jibon', '25a.jpg', '25a.flv', 'Tuesday 5:30 PM', '22 minutes', '', '', 'Ahidul Azam Tipu', '', '', 'This program is kind of a documentary. It is basically a life journey of the aged and respectable persons who has contribuyed for our society, nation and country like Kabi Shamsur RahmanBhasha Shoinik Matin, Ajit Roy, etc. This program contains an archive value.'),
(26, 4, 0, '2009-05-24', 'R Ranna', '26f.jpg', '26f.flv', 'Wednesday 07:35 PM', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Bangladeshi people are very much conscious about cooking. "R-Ranna" is a cooking based program for all type of viewers. This is completely cooking show and the presenter is Nahid Osman. Through this program viewers can get cooking related tips.'),
(27, 7, 0, '2009-05-24', 'R U Ready', '27a.jpg', '27a.flv', 'Sunday 5:30 PM', '22 Minutes', '', '', 'Prodip Vottacharjayi', 'Azra', '', 'The life is becoming very competitive. To be ready for this challenge one has to be smart as well as confident. This program is produced by Pradeep Bhat will make you ready for the challenge. To make life a daring experience you have to prepare yourself. RU Ready is all about making you fit for the next ''Headline''. Produced by Pradeep Bhat will make you ready for the challenge ahead.'),
(28, 7, 0, '2009-05-24', 'Sa Sa Dhin Tai', '28a.jpg', '28a.flv', 'Thursday 5:30 PM', '22 minutes', '', '', 'Afroza Sulatana Chaity', '', '', 'Two dearest kids present this show. Here you can keep an eye on the children''s dance, song, reciting, drama etc. Devoid of these you can get lot of kid''s related unknown information in news part. Already 52 episodes on aired and now it is presenting with more entertainment and new look for viewers.'),
