(51, 2, 0, '2010-07-03', 'Sheal Pondit', '51b.jpg', '51b.flv', 'Monday to Tuesday 10:00 PM', NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 'Written by Shahin Zaman and directed by Al Hajen, the serial is set against the backdrop of a village which is full of dacoits. The cast includes ATM Shamsuzzaman, Wahida Mollik Jolly, Chanchal Chowdhury, Nadia, AKM Hasan, Nupur, MM Morshed, Shimana and Sohel Khan.'),
