(66, 2, 0, '2010-12-31', 'Aircom', '66b.jpg', '66b.flv', 'Saturday & Sunday 9:05 PM', NULL, '', '', '', NULL, '', 'The mega serial is planned and thought by Fahmida Irfan and scripted by Iffat Arefin Tonni, while mega serial is directed by Alvi Ahmed. The cast includes Partha Barua, Shahriar Nazim Joy, Tanjika, Badhon, Agun, Tania Hossain, Alif, Sajjad Reza, Tusi and Faria.<br><br>It''s a story of country''s leading telecom service named ''Aircom.'' A group of young and talent youths are involved with this company as employees. While working in this telecom service, youths have to face a lot of hurdles to success in their life. They also have to work according to the master plan of the company. This type of mechanized and real life are focal points of this serial.'),
(67, 2, 0, '2011-01-08', 'Angshik Shada Kalo', '67.jpg', '67.flv', 'Tuesday & Wednesday 6:00 PM', NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 'Written and directed by Sayem Zafar Imami, the drama satires stalking on a campus. The cast includes Amirul Haque, Anisur Rahman Milon, Hasan Maswood, Swadin Khusru, Biddya Sinha and Farzana Chhobi Nawsaba.'),
(68, 2, 0, '2011-01-08', 'Bagh Potul', '68.jpg', '68.flv', 'Wednesday & Thursday 9:20 PM', NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 'Written by Ahmed Shabuddin and directed by Kaisar Ahmed, ''Baghputul'' features women''s struggle in male dominated society. The cast includes Shubarna Mustafa, Elora Gahar, Anisur Rahman Milon, Kusum Shikdar and Apurbha.'),
(69, 2, 0, '2011-01-08', 'Life Is Beautiful', '69b.jpg', '69b.flv', 'Friday & Saturday 9:50 PM', NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '''Life is Beautiful'' scripted by Mominul Islam and directed by Sanjit Sarkar. The cast includes Shahed Sharif Khan, Tonima Hamid, Kushum Sikder, Fazlur Rahman Babu, Dolly Zahur, SM Mohsin, Rahamat Ali, Faruk Ahmed, Dr Ezazul Islam, Afzal Sharif, Shirin Alam, Binoy Bhadra, among others.<br><br>Story of the drama serial revolves with a little educated workless person hailed from a mofussil area. He has many hopes and aims but his capability is less enough to fulfill these. He has to face many complications in his life. But he always tries to enjoy the life gets engage with those ladies who also want to enjoy their life. As a result, he has to face bad rumors and gossips in this connection.'),
(70, 2, 0, '2011-01-08', 'Tourist', '70a.jpg', '70a.flv', 'Friday to Sunday 10:00 PM', NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 'Drama serial ''Tourist'' is scripted and directed by Arun Chowdhury. The cast includes Agun, Tazin Ahmed, Naznin Chumky, Mir Sabbir, Nadia, Arefin Shuvo, Homayra Himu, Saju Khadem, Adnan Faruk Hillol, among others.<br><br>Story of the serial revolves with a tourism company. A group of tourists go to Rangamati. In the group everybody has their wife or girlfriend, but leader of this team does not have anybody, he is alone. He always tries to enjoy company of others. But at one stage he realizes that it is difficult to survive alone. After see-offing this group, the tourist company again engages to operate another group. Story of the serial continues.'),
